WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.043 --> 00:00:06.586
It's great to have your movies,
photos and music right in your hands,

00:00:06.588 --> 00:00:09.048
but sometimes you want to share
them on the big screen.

00:00:10.301 --> 00:00:14.136
AirPlay is a technology from
Apple that is build in every iPhone,

00:00:14.138 --> 00:00:16.013
iPad and iPod touch

00:00:16.015 --> 00:00:19.183
that lets you stream your
digital content to an Apple TV,

00:00:19.185 --> 00:00:21.351
an Airport Express
with connected speakers,

00:00:21.353 --> 00:00:24.605
and even wirelessly direct to 
AirPlay enable speakers.

00:00:25.025 --> 00:00:28.695
It works automatically thorough
your wi-fi network with not set up needed.

00:00:31.113 --> 00:00:33.120
Lets say you're watching your movie
on your iPad

00:00:33.121 --> 00:00:35.533
and you want see it on your HDTV

00:00:35.535 --> 00:00:38.453
just tap here and your movie
is stream instantly.

00:00:39.621 --> 00:00:41.413
You can play and pause your movie

00:00:41.415 --> 00:00:45.043
even scrub to find just the
scene you are looking for.

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:47.711
Every action you make
is reflected on the screen,

00:00:47.713 --> 00:00:49.338
and it's all wireless.

00:00:50.216 --> 00:00:52.133
When you are watching your movie on TV

00:00:52.135 --> 00:00:55.220
you can still surf the web
or check your email,

00:00:55.930 --> 00:00:57.180
or turn off the screen

00:00:57.181 --> 00:01:00.641
and sit back and control
with the Apple TV remote.

00:01:03.968 --> 00:01:06.410
Imagine you just shot some photos
on your iPhone

00:01:06.411 --> 00:01:08.218
and you want show your friends

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:11.068
with AirPlay everybody in the room
can enjoy them together.

00:01:12.988 --> 00:01:15.733
You flickr thorough your pictures
like you've got them ready in your hands

00:01:15.735 --> 00:01:18.335
only you see them on your HDTV.

00:01:18.336 --> 00:01:20.328
You can even watch your photos slideshow

00:01:20.330 --> 00:01:22.830
it's as easy as tapping to start the show.

00:01:30.173 --> 00:01:33.245
You've already got all your favorite
songs on your iPod,

00:01:33.246 --> 00:01:36.501
now you can stream them directly
to Apple TV,

00:01:36.503 --> 00:01:38.956
speakers connected to an Airport Express

00:01:40.016 --> 00:01:42.350
or any AirPlay enable speakers.

00:01:42.976 --> 00:01:44.685
You can change songs

00:01:44.686 --> 00:01:47.935
and crank the volume,
all right from your iPad,

00:01:47.936 --> 00:01:50.316
iPhone or iPod touch.

00:01:50.318 --> 00:01:53.236
And you can even stream some
other music apps like Pandora.

00:01:54.990 --> 00:01:58.245
With AirPlay technology
built into all iOS devices

00:01:58.246 --> 00:02:00.951
you can stream all the great media
that you've got in your hands

00:02:00.953 --> 00:02:03.913
to the best home video system
in your house.

